title: Mike And Michael A Friendship In Time
description:
Michael Jackson travels back to the past and befriends a boy named Mike who changes his life forever.

 Trapped between 2 worlds the past and the present as they both try to fixed each others lives that's often filled with a lot of pain, somehow they find joy and strength within each other, among all the chaos its them against the world, nothing or no one can come between. a true testament to me myself and I. A bond that only a few can understand. 2 famous superstars.

Mike a famous lead singer of the Jackson Five known as cute adorable, mature, intelligent outspoken and very wise for his age, face the difficulties of being the golden child and the heartache from his father who never was, a loss of childhood with unforgettable memories known to never exist.  if there was one person who understood it was 

Michael a mega superstar often seen as weird, genius a freak, child like and UN earthy creature not of this world like a a rare alien never seen but known to existed an aura like no other that can't always be comprehend.

Mike and Michael both cross paths with a mind of their own forming what seems like unlikely friendship both so different but so much alike .
coming together to destroy Sony a  music agency that acts like they're part of the government with so much power as they try to take them down.
 A secret that has to be kept as Mike and Michael realize they are time travels, stuck in a triangle of love and hate past and present, will they be able to fix what's forever broken or will things remain the same that was never meant to be changed.

title: Flowering In War  (ON HOLD)
description:
Book One in the War Torn series.
--

On May 16, 2010, a WWII plane wreckage is discovered in Greenland. Two days later, during the excavation and investigation, a body is found comatose, protected from the elements by the plane's body. The woman is transferred to S.H.I.E.L.D. after investigation, and nine days after her discovery, wakes up.

It is discovered that her name is Amy Lamel. Amy claims to be no one special, just someone upon whom a miracle fell. But in reality, she holds an impressive stack of accomplishments: incredible aim with most guns; well-trained in hand-to-hand combat; well-versed in engineering; a member of the Army Nurse Corps and respected medical professional; and the would-be fiance of Howard Stark, had she survived the war in the usual manner.

Now Amy has to face a world where the man she loved is dead and society has evolved, and learn how to deal with all of her experiences without giving away her true past.

One of these "rules" for living in the modern world will be broken. Whose fault it is, and how it happens? Well, that's a whole 'nother story.

title: Impecáveis - Pretty Little Liars - Vol 2 - Sara Shepard
description: 'Impecáveis' retoma a saga de Spencer Hastings, Emily Fields, Hanna Marin e Aria Montgomery na rica comunidade de Rosewood, na Pensilvânia. Após uma cerimônia em memória de Allison DiLaurentis, a amiga cujo corpo foi encontrado três anos após seu desaparecimento, as garotas descobrem que todas estavam recebendo mensagens de texto e emails assinados por 'A', ameaçando revelar seus mistérios mais íntimos. Como desconfiavam que Ali poderia estar viva e ser a responsável pelos recados, elas sentem uma mistura de muita tristeza e alívio com a confirmação de sua morte. Mas 'A' continua a atormentar cada uma das meninas e, desesperadas para descobrir a verdade, elas ficam chocadas ao ver que Toby Cavanaugh, irmão de Jenna, voltou à cidade.

title: Arabella Park: Season 1
description:
[A WATTPAD FEATURED STORY/highest ranking: #30 Mystery/Thriller] I've included this special gift of flesh. It is an assurance to you that she is currently mine and I will do with her what I will until I see the money.

 Everyone knows that losing friends is a natural part of the high school experience.  Yet, what happens when a friend doesn't intentionally "go ghost" but is abruptly taken away?
         Kameron, Grayson, Mikey, Yasmin, and Jenna have been thick as thieves from childhood. Rightfully so-they make up the American minority in the German twin city of Arabella Park. When one of the five suddenly turns up missing, the remaining friends must find a way to bring her back while keeping up the facade of leading ordinary small-town lives. 
        As they search for their missing friend, they discover things about themselves and one another that will catapult them into an explosive climax and the ultimate revelation of who done it.
        A multi-faceted mystery, Arabella Park brings to life what it means to endure the most frightful, profound time of one's life-the teenage years-while being stretched to the limits of what it means to be an adult, even a hero.

title: Sin Nombre, Sin Rostro
description:
Trey has been changing names and faces since he became an official member of the group. And yes, Trey, is not his real name, and his face, is not his original face. But he liked this one, this particular identity. So for years, he has been Trey. Just Trey.

Besides, he wants to forget what happened to Tomoyuki, Mark, Carlos, James and his other identities. They remind him of a past he tries to erase.

But can he really forget something that shaped him for who he is right now? Can he escape a life he did not choose but was born into?

And who is he really?
Tomoyuki?
Mark?
Carlos?
James?
Trey?

Who is he trying to kid?

He is not Trey.

He is no one.

He is a man with No Name, No Face.

title: World Lost
description:
Who knew humanity would be playing Hide-and-Seek with cannibalistic maniacs as the seekers. I don't know what I did to deserve something that went as far as the end of the world; what any of us humans had done. A world that once had a future in store now had fallen into a world without hope. Without peace. A world that was lost. 

Maybe we had driven the world to what lie beneath the iceberg ourselves. Maybe mad scientists fooled around too much. The truth was that no one knew, and probably would ever know. One thing is for sure, though. I would not live another day just to be turned into a murderer. I will survive in the world with no future; the world lost among itself.

title: Whiskey
description:
"How could even think of rejecting me? I'm gorgeous," the obviously arrogant boy said.
 
"Lucky for me, I wasn't even thinking of getting with you," I said sourly.

I winked and walked away from him, swaying my hips with every step, making half the boys at this party stop and stare. 

Passing Maya, I skipped over to the bar. I looked over at her, winked, and downed another shot of Whiskey. 

--------------------

It was a game Arden and her best friend created. 
For the whole summer, they could only get drunk off Whiskey, no getting drunk off love. 

It worked. Everything was turning out fine, until one night at a house party when everything went crazy. Shots were taken, secrets were told, things happened. 


He was her light when all she saw was darkness. When she was stuck in a horrible place, outside her friend's house, completely drunk, with nowhere to go.

She is Arden Smith.
He is Apollo Tyler.

This is their story.

title: Life Isn't How It Seems
description:
"You don't understand Jacob!  I love you, and as weird as that sounds coming from me,  I'm being one hundred and ten percent honest.  I have never once loved someone more in my lif-" Ally tried to say, but Jacob cut her off with a passionate kiss. 

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Jacob is a screwed up boy,  he's never had friends,  he doesn't talk,  he doesnt go to school, he dropped school to work instead, and when he goes home he plays his piano.  His life at home is not the best,  he hates it, he wants to escape, but after he meets this girl, his life changes, Jacob seems, happier? What is this feeling? He's never felt anything other than pain, regret, hate,  and depression, but happiness? 

Ally is the complete opposite of Jacob, she's happy,  she has plenty of friends at school, she loves music.  She's never felt sadness, or regret, or pain. When she meets Jacob, her life changes, she wants to help him, but he refuses help. She connects with him, and they grow great affection towards each other. 

But something happens to Jacob and Ally,  they become lost, she pushes away all of her friends, she loses connection with her family, and keeps herself locked up in her room. Did she change for the better? Or did she change for the worse?

title: A Skye's Limit
description:
Born with a father who hates her.

Blamed for things she never did.

Given magic she doesn't understand.

She's broken. She's upset.

But she's not afraid to fight back. 

Meet Skye, a young Phoenix who lives with two of her closet and best friends, Robin and Wolf. Saved from a house which was burning in a "wildfire", Robin has taken care of Skye since she was an infant. 

Now Skye is older and is in more danger than she's ever known possible. She's being hunted and blamed for terrible crimes; ones she never commited. 

This is a story of strength. This is a story of happiness and sadness in the darkest parts of Skye's life. This is a story of going beyond expectations.

This is A Skye's Limit.

A Skye's Limit is book #2 in the fantastic Fantasy/Adventure series, Phoenix Territory.

title: Rise of the Warlords
description:
Across the lands in the East, 3 kingdoms are on the brink of war as warlords from different dominions fight each other to dominate a divided land.

Meanwhile, a lone swordsman, seeking a peaceful life, finds himself involved in the war again as the warlords attempted to take him as their weapon.

Later, a group of martial artists and ancient wise men pursue a journey to end the war by teaching the art of Kung Fu so peace can return. But their teaching is thwarted by the war itself and they are forced to fight back.

And finally, an army of elite warriors defend the warring kingdoms from the coming threats in the West, South and North.

All of these occurring events will someday shake the very land itself.

But a question lies within the minds of the people in the 3 kingdoms: will peace return or disappear?

title: Making It Up
description:
One day Mason was walking in the woods, in his wolf form, when somebody came up and attacked him. They fought for a little while until, Mason had the other wolf on his back and paw on his stomach ready to rip his heart out, he recognized the wolf as a Convel, a beta family, he quickly got up into his human form and the other wolf did too. The other wolf smelled the air and so did Mason recognizing the smell as his childhood beta. Aaron Convel. He looked at him and vamp speeded away since he was in his wolf form. Leaving his childhood beta standing there speechless. 

Go on the adventure with Mason and his childhood pack as he finds a way too live his old life, and keep his old one normal at the same time.

title: Captured and Loved By The Unknown Wolf
description:
"I loved you and you were taken and hidden from me." He said. "But now I am back and I am not letting you out of my sight."

I glared at him. I thought I had gotten rid of him long ago. But he's back and still wants the same thing. This guy can't take a hint.

"I have news for you. I have a Mate. I am not interested." I said.

He smiled and said "Oh you are cute when you're mad. That's what I love about you, sweetheart."

I have had just about enough of him. I shifted into my wolf form and I ran at him.

----------------------------------------------------------

Aria has left her old pack with her Mate, Lucas Moon. He is the Alpha and she is his Luna. 

Aria has been through a lot the last few years and has met and defeated many enemies. She is the best fighter and never runs from a fight. She's even come from the edge of death. 

Lucas is the Alpha of The Moon Pack. With Aria now in his life, everything is perfect. But ever since she came back from the edge of death, she hasn't been the same. And on top of that, there is an enemy who puts Lucas's pack and Lucas's title as Alpha, to the test.

In a story where old memories are remembered and old faces are known. Aria and Lucas will have to be on the alert. Ladies and Gentlemen. I present the sequel to "My Past Mate Rejected Me."

with four powerful rulers. The kingdoms are separated into the four main elements that consist Fire, Earth, Air, and Water. Each ruler was born with a gift of each one of the four elements, breeding them to be immortal. These rulers were made to maintain the balance of the world. 

Evanora is a daughter of two uneducated parents with her home living down in a small town. She spends her days wandering around the streets and daydreaming about the powerful gods and goddesses that rule above them all - a story her father tells every night for a bedtime story. Little does she know her life is  just about to begin in a world of mighty rulers and golden thrones.

Have you ever heard that our lives are intertwined, by two people linked to another, even if we don't know we exist, young and old we effect then somehow. title: Captive
description:
Imagine having a catchy tune stuck in your head for a whole day. You would want to take your mind off it. 

Right?

Right. 

That's what Athena wanted to do.

So she went for a walk and got lost...

Just when she thinks she found hope of returning back home she gets kidnapped. 

Athena can be stupid but this girl has got guts. She figures away to escape but being cocky is in her personality. So, she wants to brag to her kidnappers. When she does, they come looking for her. 

She didn't know that she crossed a territory that was not hers to cross.

Soon, her kidnappers kidnap her again. Only, this time it's harder to escape. She's locked in a dungeon all alone. 

She doesn't know, that she's going into unfamiliar territory (literally and figuratively). 

ONE MORE THING, SHE FINDS HER SOUL MATE! 

NO, ITS NOT NUTELLA OR OREOS OR ANY OTHER TYPE OF FOOD. HER MATE...

Read on to accompany her on her journey. Stay with her through thick and thin. It's about to be a long ride...but it's just the beginning.

title: My Ex Nextdoor
description:
Ano ang mararamdaman mo 'pag iniwan ka ng paasa mong boyfriend na wala man lang sinabing dahilan sa'yo? Well, 95% sure na magagalit ka 'diba?

Syempre, sino nga ba naman ang hindi magagalit 'pag iniwan ka na lang ng boyfriend mo sa ere. Pero ika nga nila, 'Love is in the air' daw kaya tayo iniiwan ng magagaling nating boyfriend pero hindi naman talaga literal ang ibig sabihin nun. 

Nakakainis lang kasi minahal natin sila ng PAK na PAK pero iniwan lang tayo ng GANERN GANERN lang. Aminin niyo, minsan nyo na ring naisipan na basagin ang kaligayahan ng boyfriend niyo at gawing scramble egg saka ipakain sa alagang aso ng kapit bahay niyo para lang maramdaman nila ang sakit na ibinigay nila sa inyo, right? Minsan niyo na rin hinihiling na sana mawala na sila sa mundong 'to o 'di kaya sana hindi nyo na makikita ang pangit na pag-mumukha ng boyfriend nyo, right? 

Pero what if isang araw... Magigising ka na lang at magugulat na kapit bahay mo na pala ang isang lalake na kinamumuhian mo sa buong buhay mo? Hmmm. Ano kaya ang mararamdaman mo? 

Kung kailan 100% sure na moved on ka na, bigla-bigla na lang susulpot ang paasa mong boyfriend. Sarap bayagan ano? 

Anyways, napapahaba na ang description ng storyang ito. 

Oh siya. Simulan niyo ng basahin ang storyang ito! Enjoy!

Note: Ang storyang ito ay punong-puno ng ka-bitter-an dahil narin sa karanasan ng ating bida na isa sa mga naging sawi ang lovelife at naiwan nang mag-isa sa ere.

title: A Twist in Time [Harry Potter Roleplay]
description:
Okay, this is the last time I'm attempting this. If it dies this time, the idea is gone for good. 

Time flies, seasons change, the world goes on. Time pauses for no one. The future is always coming and the past is always behind us, but what people forget is that time has always been and always will be relative. 

The Marauders' future is the Golden Trio's present, which is the Next Generation's past. They all have a connected destiny. 

Through Voldemort's dark magic, time becomes more confusing and fates aline. The Golden Trio's Era finds itself together with the Mauraders and the Next Gen. They all exist together, outside of time. How will people react? What will happen next? Or perhaps, it's already happened.

description:
As soon as her mother goes missing and the only clue pointing to her whereabouts is her search history, Elise Newman has packed her bag and boarded the first flight to Japan. When her trip goes awry, Elise is pitted against her own fears and whatever is lurking in the forest as she finds just how far she would go to save someone she loves...and if she can even save herself in the process.

title: Ink | Namjin
description:
"It's common sense. Everyone knows about it - you'd be stupid not to. Some people hate it. Some people love it. Some people admire other's talents, yet others wish that the stupid drawings never appeared on their arms. Personally, I find it stupid. My arms - they're always bare. As if whoever is destined to be mine doesn't want to ever find their soulmate. That's why they're always bare. And I can't do anything about it."

A world in which one draws on their arm, and their soulmate has it appear on their arm. But Kim Namjoon doesn't believe in it - his arms have always been bare, other for the doodles drawn on his arm by himself out of boredom, because it seems like his soulmate will never make any attempts at trying to find him. 

Or that was what Namjoon believed.

title: My Cold Heart
description:
My cold Heart

Aurora Morreti was once a sweet and innocent girl, after her husband -Sebastian Vetrov- betrayed her by sleeping around with other women throughout their marriage and lying about loving her, she became a cold-hearted person. 

When Aurora found out what her husband was doing, she left. Without leaving behind a clue of where to find her. It was like she just evaporated. 

Aurora left hurt, heart broken, and her cheating bastard of a husband's seed in her. 

Many years went by, Sebastian looked for Aurora because according to him she was the one and only thing he loved in the world. But he failed to find her. 

What will happen when Aurora comes back to town to visit her dying mother, with Sebastian's replica by her side? Will she ever forgive him? Will he ever forgive her for keeping his child from him?

Read My Cold Heart to find out what happens next.

title: Moving On.
description:
This was not supposed to happen, they were not supposed to meet. An angry young Pashtun with his ego problems was not supposed to fall for the Americanized version of a Pakistani Muhajir, hack life was not decided for love, not for him at least.
He was hard headed than why his gray orbs sudden soften for the brown ones. He had decided that he will marry the first girl that came in front of him to prove a point to his theoretically former tribal bride and in laws. But it took a highway route when he saw a certain, lost girl at the Jinnah Airport. A girl in white cotton floor length dress with a brown leather jacket with a pair of converse munching on a packet of lays masala, sitting on her own trolley, flipping her head here and there as her scarf moved with her without even for once being displaced from its original position.
Was he ready to marry a girl that he does not know let alone liked by first sight when he knew in his family approval comes from the elders where there is no choice left for them, the broods? He might be an introvert and an honor preserving chap but he was clear when it came to what he wants and needs. He never confused his feelings with his duties as the head of his family or as the impending head of the chief of his tribe, to be the next Emir of Gorgush. 
Olasyar Khan, was in that state of mind but then why did his heart feel that pine? He was ready to make everything turn according to his desires, the Pashtun in him was not ready to back down and let others lead his life for him. Allah showed him the way, so he will move all the rocks and stones in his path even if he must pick them up by his bare hands.
As the tag on the bag read the name, he uttered the last words and left, "Zareen Wadi, be ready to be Zareen Khan."
Their fates were already amalgamated, they just had to find their way to each other.

title: She'll be OKAY
description:
She'll be okay.
At lease that's what she tells herself. 


Growing up I always told myself; head up, stand tall, and smile through the pain. That's what got me through most of my life. 

It has always been my mom, my sister and I. But technically it was only me, myself, and I. Mother always working, Sister moved out, and I living in the land of the forgotten. 

Being that I had daddy issues since birth, that meant he was always out the picture. But to me it only meant one more person out the picture. 

Love isn't real it's just the excuse people use to have sex. But when "love" create another human being must people tend to get scared and run like the wind. 

But what happens when Cupid tried to pull that love game on the one person who doesn't believe in love. 


I am Veronica Queens and this is my story...........

title: Lonely Together
description:
When I saw her for the first time, a strange feeling came over me, at first I couldn't quite place it. Now I know it was a mixture of surprise and anticipation. 
I didn't made much out of it at first, but I still couldn't get her off my head. How often does one finds a girl walking alone on a deserted road, wearing a black tight dress, high hells and dragging a dusty jacket. 
I couldn't see much of her face, but the only glimpse I had was enough to make my stomach tightened. 
She didn't looked lost, or helpless, instead it looked like she knew exactly where she was going, it looked like she was on her way towards something.

title: The Secret of Drulea Cottage
description:
"I shall always love you, my dear bairn. Remember that, no matter what happens. And you must promise me something before I go," Bethany whispered with all the strength she could muster.

"Anything, Mum," the young woman answered.

"You must stay away from the water."

"I promise."

The year is 1759. Briony Fairborn, midwife of Everton, struggles to find acceptance after her mother's death while living in a town that ostracizes her for her scandalous origins. Her family has always been shrouded in mystery, ever since her great-grandmother first came to the small town in Orkney. With only one friend in the world, she has little hope of gaining any others, let alone finding a husband. Her life seems set on a straight course without any room for wavering.

That is, until an unexpected ship finds its way to Everton's port.

Suddenly, Briony's life becomes much more complicated. These newcomers are hiding something, and Briony soon discovers that they are not the only ones. A strange man named Niall Moreland arrives in town, a man who offers Briony the acceptance she craves. But does he know something about her family that she doesn't?

And what about the charming owner of the ship, Santiago Mendes? His interest in Briony seems to go beyond mere friendship, but could he ever love someone like her?

As Briony seeks the truth, the secrets of her heritage begin to unravel. Secrets that she may not be ready to face.

title: Against Her Wishes
description:
"You should be grateful for this opportunity, Charlotte. That is another thing you'll learn some day." She said, and I knew she meant to end the conversation on that note. I no longer wanted to be in her presence anyways, but my legs refused to carry me away from the woman I used to admire. My mother was my rock, the one I could count on to stick up for me in any way possible. We struggled through everything together. Now, I could hardly look at her without scowling. 
     "Thank you, Mother, for accepting the opportunity to sign away my life. I'm sure I'll be grateful someday, if I haven't already killed myself." I said, then quickly turned on my heel and stormed out of the room. I could hardly see through the blind rage that clouded my vision, but I managed to get into my room, lock the door, and throw myself face first onto my still unmade bed.
     Letting out the sob I'd been holding in, my body violently shook as I cried for the first time since my father had died. Never have I felt there to be a reason to feel so weak, until now. Knowing that my fate was sealed to a man whom I've never met made my stomach throb and throat constrict painfully. In the end, this was be the only thing my mother ever raised me for after all. And that revelation was the hardest part to swallow. 
***
February 27, 1845
     After attending the illustrious Woodvale ball, Charlotte is given devastating and life altering news that changes her own predetermined path forever. Except, this decision doesn't come without its consequences. Follow a young woman as she struggles to grow close to someone she feels she shouldn't have affection towards, whilst also learning to love herself in return. Yet, tragedy and incredible heartbreak still lurk in the depths of Charlotte's uncertain future...

title: Looking for the Lighthouse
description: My mom used to tell me that lighthouses were like beacons of hope. We would travel every summer up the east coast to Maine and stop at all the lighthouses we could find. My mom went missing with my dad at the start of my senior year and since then things have gone down hill. I have to find them but I have no idea where to start. It's the summer after my senior year and while I have plans for the future, I still feel lost and without purpose. I guess you could say I need my own lighthouse right about now. Come fall, I'll be a freshman at Brown but until then I have the summer to figure out who I am and how my life got to where it is.  But with a new mysterious guy, and two amazing best friends who've planned a summer full of adventure, maybe my chances aren't all that bad.

title: Bittersweet Kisses
description:
What would you do if the very person you wanted to destroy, starts to win over you heart?
___

You know Quinn Demitrius, everyone does. Perhaps you've seen her on the covers of Vogue, on the TV wining a Grammy or even shopping on fifth Avenue with her beloved sisters. She's Hollywood's hottest starlet, and the things she did to become the name on everyone's lips are merely stains on the pavement beneath her Prada heels.

Sebastian Bishop, the mysterious actor with an even more confusing past. Sebastian has a hitlist, but not the murder kind. Instead he has a list of people who he's hell bent on destroying with Quinn's Demitrius name written in red underline. 

With the rest if Hollywood's golden brat pack, an entire fake relationship, a mysterious blogger exposing Hollywood's elites dirty laundry, drama, scandals,cute moments and a sinful amount of bittersweet kisses.

Bittersweet Kisses is a story bound to tug on your heartstrings.

title: Dark Souls Cheese Strategies: Cheesy Souls 1/2/3
description: This book is a guide on ways to cheese bosses in the "Dark Souls" games. "Cheesing" means to defeat a boss with as little effort as possible, without the cheese being harder than the actual fight. For example, standing in an arena and doing nothing as you watch the boss fall off a ledge and die, due to your character's position. This guide should be getting updated a lot, and if anyone has advice on cheese strats it would greatly appreciated that you share in the comments. Even if the strategy is already written for a boss, alternative strategies are welcome, and thus will be tested and added if it is legitimate.

title: An Unusual Mate
description:
Brooklyn Kelly or Brooke for short is a part of the Talkeetna Shifter Clan in Alaska because she is a shifter. She can shift into a Snow Leopard that is rather feral in character meaning the Brooklyn has little to no control over whatever her Leopard does meaning that not many people would see her as a good mate. As such Brooklyn has pretty much given up on ever finding her true mate because she wouldn’t be able to accept him as her mate because of her Snow Leopard. What really annoys her though is that the way her Snow Leopard is now wasn’t caused by her genetics it was caused by her rubbish upbringing along with her two sibling’s upbringing. 
When Loki the God of Mischief is quite literally dumped onto the clan’s doorstep Brooklyn begins to feel things that she wouldn’t have even thought she could feel and the same goes for her Snow Leopard. Well at first Brooklyn ignores Loki pretty much and argues with him to no end but as time goes on and they begin to become friends Brooklyn soon realises that her feelings for Loki are set deep within herself.
But when S.H.I.E.L.D finds out that Loki is in Alaska and has been accepted into the clan all hell basically breaks loose with Nick Fury sending the Avengers to retrieve Loki. But when Brooklyn also gets caught up in the cross fire and is taken back to S.H.I.E.L.D her Leopard turns rouge and Brooklyn looses all control and she can’t even shift back. Nick Fury eventually agrees to let Loki in with the already rouge Snow Leopard only to see if she can be calmed down.
What will happen to Brooklyn? Will she calm down? Will Loki be allowed to remain a part of the clan?
Warning: Contains a very expressive woman who swears like a sailor. A sarcastic God of Mischief. A very aggressive Snow Leopard and some scenes of the sexual nature.

title: Reality Breaker
description: A boy, Kall Azuki found his life mostly at school and his room. On his way to become a shut-in-NEET, he mysteriously finds himself in a situation. On the day of his birthday, he goes out to eat with his Cousin, Karona Ashii. Walking, he tripped over a book, and picked it up. In spite of this, Karona texts him to be there quicker otherwise he'll be dining alone tonight. At home he finds it falling out of his jacket pocket, and digs deeper to what this book holds. He opens it and finds  his name and a page that says... "Put your hand here!". Of course, you wouldn't do it would you? He does it anyway. Ink starts spewing out all over his hand. Slowly creeping up his arm. He finds himself trapped in which he can't escape. The ink slowly goes all over his body, until all you could ever see was the dark. He wakes a little bit later to find... its morning and, a girl... is on top of him?! I wonder whats to become of this, right Sae? (No not really... Ka-Ki! You said this would be fun!) title: Divided
description:
SEQUEL TO UNITED

"This is not a civil war." 

"Then what is it?"

"The end of the Avengers Initiative." 
***
It's been almost two years since the Revengers first landed their ship on Midgard. New recruits have joined the Avengers, while Asgard thrives in secrecy, shrouded from the rest of the Earth. Overall, it's been an eventful,  but memorable two years. Everyone is finally happy.

That is, until two brothers discover the Eye of Agamotto, and a way to bring Frigga back to life. Traveling in time, of course, has its undesirable effects, and Thor and Loki soon find themselves trapped on Asgard while the Avengers are nothing more than broken memories of the past. 

One thing is for certain. Even if they are able to restore their original timeline, they must live with the knowledge that one thing is for certain.

Nothing will ever be the same again.

title: Grabbing Your Hand, Dragging you Away
description:
I am a princess, moreover, I am a fool of a princess.

Born in the imperial palace, my appearance is as average as that of the white radish and cabbages in the fields. Throughout the four seasons of the year, my face is always displaying a dull expression, eyes forever shrouded in haze.

But in reality, I know of the secrets within this palace.

Including hers, his, and theirs.

Just leisurely living my days comfortably in the palace like this, I firmly believe I can continue to play dumb to the end.

Taking your hand, dragging you away. Not leaving you say? Very well, close the doors and release the hounds. (Expressionless face)

⁃⁃⁃❖⁃⁃⁃
  
"Where do you think you are going?" Locaine's lips are mere inches from my ear. A shiver traveling from the base of my spine to the strait of my neck at his hypnotic voice.

"I don't want to play this type of game with you," my voice falters briefly, thoughts raking through my mind at the many possibilities to the outcome of succumbing to him. 

Locaine backs off me more or less, only to toss me around, pushing my back up against the door. His sculpted chest presses against mine as he flashes me a coy smile, "I haven't even explained the game yet and you already want to leave."

She wants to live a normal life where she can go to school, have friends who will be there for her and she will be there for them. But then one day, Joker comes up with a plan that wasn't like the rest. Not at all. He was going to kill Robin. She wants out, and maybe, just maybe, he can help her and she can help him. Will she finally have a shot at a new life? 

I DO NOT OWN JOKER, HARLEY QUINN, BATMAN, ROBIN, ALFRED, OR ANY OTHER CHARACTERS, SETTINGS, OR SIMILARITIES IN STORY LINES OR PLOTS BELONGING TO THE WONDERFUL DC UNIVERSE! THOSE ARE ALL THIER IDEAS AND CHARACTERS! I ONLY OWN LESLIE AND HER STORY! DO NOT STEAL HER OR MY STORY LINE. THANK YOU.

Thalia and her brother arrive at Daphne's and she claims she's one of the other Oracles. Blaire Collins has a curse.

<<<<<<< HEAD
A curse that goes by the name of clumsiness.

Despite being confident and bold, she tumbles over anything and everything; whether it's furniture or air, Blaire is almost positive that no one can beat her when it comes to her eternal embarrassment of being a klutz. 

So, when her so-called 'curse' causes her to trip onto River Knight, the academy's richest student, and end up locking lips with him, Blaire is absolutely mortified and is sure that the rest of her life will end up with her digging herself into a hole and never coming out. 

After all, a boy like him is sure to take every chance he can get to embarrass her over the incident, right?

Wrong.

Instead of doing what most people would do, River decides to befriend the clumsy yet confident girl.

And somewhere along the way, he realizes that maybe another kiss with her won't be so bad.

title: Transported To Another World Because Of A Suspicious Auction Item
description:
Rexi Siegfried and Charlotte Banister lives in a world where espers exist. Espers are people with unique abilities that range from controlling fire to seeing the future. 

Rexi and Charlotte are espers, and they were just enjoying life before their friend, Nao Yamagata, a genius in the science field but also an otaku, brought them an item she got from an auction.

Cause that just isn't suspicious right?

Nao tested it out, and it ended up transporting Rexi and Charlotte into another world. 

As Nao desperately tries to find a way to get her precious friends back to their own world, Rexi and Charlotte needs to adopt to the new world that is greatly different from theirs.

But what they don't know is that they've been transported into a world that has the exact same settings as an otome game that Nao has played before.

What will happen when two unplanned characters appear in an otome game where every event was planned out?

title: El Dia Que Se Perdió La Cordura - Javier Castillo
description:
Amor, odio, destino, extrañas prácticas, intriga y acción trepidante inundan las páginas de una novela que se ha convertido en todo un fenómeno editorial antes de su publicación en papel.

«A veces el destino nos pone a prueba para que sepamos que existe».

Centro de Boston, 24 de diciembre, un hombre camina desnudo con la cabeza decapitada de una joven. El doctor Jenkins, director del centro psiquiátrico de la ciudad, y Stella Hyden, agente de perfiles del FBI, se adentrarán en una investigación que pondrá en juego sus vidas, su concepción de la cordura y que los llevará hasta unos sucesos fortuitos ocurridos en el misterioso pueblo de Salt Lake diecisiete años atrás.

Atribuyo todos los derechos de autor a Javier Castillo.

title: Two Types of Fall
description:
There are two types of fall in the category of love: 

First is falling in love. Ito ata ang pinaka mabagsik na type nang fall. Kahit sino, tinatamaan, walang pinipili, walang inaayawan. 

Second is fall out of love. This type of fall commonly happens to couples, those who have labels, o nasa isang relationship. And, there are also two types of people when they fall out of love. First are those who are willing to stay. Second are those who are honest and will leave you behind.

You? What's your current situation? Isa ka ba sa mga taong nasa stage nang falling in love, o isa dun sa mga taong na fall out of love na?

title: The Bad Boy's Thorn
description:
Malia Tate returns back to her old town after two years. She was no longer the cute chubby girl with bright pink braces and large black rimmed glasses. She's back and better than ever.

She coincidentally crosses paths her former best friend Archer Silva who ditched her for popularity - he too has gone through a change.

He was no longer the rather chubby boy with a round face and coconut hairstyle. His appearance changed massively, his hair was now styled into a quiff, enhancing the colour of his tousled brown hair. His facial structures were more defined.

Malia has plans for Archer and the rest of her former high-school classmates, she wanted them to realise how it felt to be left out.

-

This is not just any revenge story, it's a journey filled with poisonous backstabbers and hypocritical, petty high-school students.

One day she goes out with her friend Lilac. Then she finds some mysterious jewels called The Jewels of Mother V.I. 

She was told that mother V.I. hid her jewels so it didn't fall into the wrong hands. Donatella bought it and wore it to school the next day.

During her lunch time she finds 18 year old Jake Roberts being troubled by Marcy. 

She saves him from getting in trouble. At the library he finds out that Donatella has a secret that is hurting her.

Then Donatella gets a warning that someone is after her and the jewels and that she needs to return to Mother V.I. Jake goes with her and the both start to fall deep in love with each other.

What will happen when Jake learns Donatella's secret? What challenges will they face? Will they make it to Mother V.I.?

title: Balkis, reine de Sa loi
description:
Je m'appelle Balkis Lawd. J'ai vingt-quatre ans.

J'aime... un peu raconter ma vie. Beaucoup la confrontation. Passionnément  mon travail en tant qu'agent secret. À la folie la vie que j'ai eu avec l'amour de ma vie. Le problème c'est que... je n'aime pas du tout l'amour. 

Je suis sûrement brisée, sûrement joyeuse. Mais par-dessus tout, n'essaye pas de me manquer de respect.

Contrairement à ce que tu peux penser, mon histoire n'est pas à l'eau de rose. J'ai déjà vécu ainsi mais ce temps est révolu. Maintenant l'eau est devenue plus rouge.

***

« - Je t'en supplie tu dois me croire quand je dis que ce n'é...

- Stop. J'en ai assez entendu. J'aurais jamais cru qu'attendre un homme était pire qu'attendre une peine de mort. Au moins un prisonnier sait à quoi il va faire face. Toi ce n'est qu'un putain de poignard dans le dos que tu as pris soin d'enfoncer dans le cœur que je t'avais donné. »

***

Salut :) Contenu pour adulte j'pense hein. C'est un roman d'amour juste un peu spécial peut-être. Et faut pas être trop trop sensible parce que je me suis dégoûtée moi-même des fois héhé..

title: The Unseen Immortal
description:
Blood. Pain. War. Those three words described his life. He never had the greed that tainted the good men of his city. And yet, he still suffered the consequences.

Perseus was a young peasant of the city, Athens. It was one of the last still Greek cities still standing. His mother was gone; she died during battle. The Persians had raided their city, leaving rubble and smoke. 

Now, Perseus had run, not because he was a coward, but to save what little he had left. His little sister.

They were different. That much their mother had told them. They were set apart. Even from each other. 

Perseus was a son of a Lelantos, the Titan of Air and Hunting. 

Phoebe, Percy's sister, was a daughter of Poseidon, the Olympian God of the Sea.

Perseus fought for his sister. Nearly died for her several times. 

Until he failed.

He was left desolate, empty, and alone.

But maybe it was for the better.

title: Hunk
description:
"Go to my room and wait for me there." His words kept playing in my mind like a CD. I was now in his room, everything was dark outside and inside too. Nobody knew I was here except for Aiden. I've no idea why he wanted me in his room when his girlfriend was sitting right next to him. I had my back facing the door and suddenly I felt someone closing the door and walking near me. My heart dropped in my stomach when I turned and suddenly found myself being pushed on the wall.

"Wh---" I tried to ask while shaking uncontrollably but his beautiful hawk eyes shut me up. 

"Why were you looking at my lips in the party?" His question shook me, I didn't know he notice. I didn't mean to but he was my long time crush and it takes time to crush those feelings. 

"i--" I stammered,

"You wanna taste them?" he walked closer, keeping his hands on the wall and locking me inside his arms, we were barely an inch away. "tell me you want that." there was a smirk on his face and suddenly it disappeared  when he looked at my lips and gulped. All I knew was that he had rejected me,  hurt me and now this? when he is already dating his long time love. 

"I'm allowing you." his words choice was terrific, giving me goosebumps.

title: Jasper || Jasper Dursley
description:
Mr. and Mrs. Dursley, of number four, Privet Drive, were proud to say that they were perfectly normal, thank you very much. They were the last people you'd expect to be involved in anything strange or mysterious, because they just didn't hold with such nonsense.

Jasper knew that, so when he came down to breakfast the morning of his birthday and saw a strange looking letter being shoved through the mail slot, he hid it. He hid the next one that came, and the next one, until he had run out of spaces to put them. He didn't read them, he could never bring himself to, so they sat untouched from the moment they were crammed behind his wardrobe. 

When the giant man comes for his cousin, Jasper hesitantly reads his own letter, and before he knows it he is whisked off into a world with people on broomsticks and talking portraits, leaving his family behind. He thinks it's amazing, but maybe the safety of his family would have been a good thing to have as things take a turn for the worse.

description:
• • •

✖️C O M P L E T E D✖️

• • •

I stared at the helmeted guy, who quickly stood up. "Watch where you're--" He shouted angrily, but stopped short.

I looked at the guy, confused as he stood there, staring at me through his blacked-out helmet.

Then, in a swift motion, he wrapped his arms around me tightly. I screamed, pushing myself off of him.

He released me, stepping back a bit. He stared back at me, confused. He quickly pulled off his helmet to reveal his face. I looked at the brown-haired boy, frozen for what felt like the hundredth time today.

"Brant?"

• • •

The bad boy with a heart (sort of), and the good girl with a traumatic past...

All is well in Konoha Minato and Kushina never died, Orochimaru never left, Itachi is still in the village, and the akatsuki never existed. The fourth hokage is standing proud and everyone in Konoha is relatively peaceful

After seeing her mother killed before her very eyes at the age of just 3 years old,  Hinata had awakened her byakugan and killed the man responsible on the spot. 3 years pass and she has a reputation as the Hyuga Prodigy to everyone in ANBU and is very close the other Prodigy in Konoha, Sakura Haruno. Will they be able to pull threw their hardships together or will they both just leave Konoha?

title: The Chronicles of Emberstone (First Draft)
description:
It has been five years since the disappearance of Prince Embrand. Throughout the provinces of Emberstone, the people grow restless, and the sudden death of King Halbard adds to their uncertainty. Baron Aldon of the Emard Province is made king in a hasty coronation, and his daughter Julienne becomes the new princess heir.

Rumors of assassination and intrigue follow them from the moment they set foot in the royal castle.  The royal court is rife with division, and in the country some of the people are beginning to gather to protest the succession of a new ruling family when the old one has not been proved ended. Then word comes that the Prince has at last been found, and the kingdom joyfully prepares to crown the son of Halbard as their rightful king.

There is just one problem... the Prince is an impostor.

Only Julienne can prove the true identity of the Prince, but her word alone is not enough to quell the hope his recovery has kindled in the people. Desperate to save the kingdom she loves from the intrigues of an unknown traitor, she turns to long-forgotten legends, seeking for a relic of the days when magic still flowed through the land. The Stone of Truth can prove her suspicions and reveal the impostor, but only if she can find it.

title: Muggle-worthy | GINNY WEASLEY
description:
Quinton Granger was very much like his younger sister, Hermione Jean Granger, well known for his studious nature among peers. However, there was a significant difference between the two, unlike Hermione, Quinton didn't possess magic.

He was a muggle.

Arthur Weasley has always been fascinated by muggles and their lifestyle, so when he meets Quinton one year as the older brother drops Hermione off at King's Cross, the two strike up a conversation about the function of a rubber duck. The two became fast friends and Quinton becomes a regular at the Burrow whenever his sister is invited over.

Ginny is trying to come to terms with her feelings over the Boy-Who-Lived, who doesn't pay her any sort of mind outside of being Ron's little sister. Hermione gives her the advice not to pine over Harry, that she should look at other boys, although when Hermione suggested it, she wasn't exactly suggesting her older brother.

It started off as letters between the two while Ginny is at school and becomes something each time the two see each other again.

Plot credits go to the amazing Pseudonymphadora ❤

title: Diary of a Dreamer
description:
"What are you?" He asked in awe.

I smiled, "I'm a dreamer."

"A what?" He asked, face scrunched up in confusion.

I just shook my head. "Look up and find out."

And he did.

He never was the same after that, neither was she, nor anyone else with the right of mind to look up at the starry sky above. 

Because a sky of twinkling lights is the spark in the darkness. 

One look is all it takes to realize you hold a spark inside of you, too.

And it's time to let it burn brighter.

title: In between {Theo Raeken}
description:
Hi I'm Davina Stilinski ,yes Stiles' twin sister. I'm just a normal girl , or so I thought. I do weird things  like I can do weird stuff with my eyes . But it all makes sense when they finally tell me . On the day we have to sign out names for all the seniors ,  I hear noises , like grunts and I follow them to see things I wouldn't expect from my closes friends,

 "We were just trying to keep you safe !"  I snort , "Yeah by sneaking around and not telling me , don't you know the best way to keep someone safe is to tell them what's happening !"

But one person stands out , but I can't be with him when I find out he's the one hurting people . But why is it that the bad guy is always the one that kills you . Or in this case a were-wolf , and a hot one too. But at least he doesn't keep me in the dark .

But in the end I'll have to pick a side , because I can't be in between .








WARNING: I DO NOT OWN ANYONE BUT DAVINA STILINSKI.

title: Catastrophe
description:
Why do people talk to me about innocence like it's something I possess? 

Men constantly strut around, acting as if they are saving me from something, when all they are doing is making themselves feel less disgusting. 

You can't take my innocence, Sir. For it's already been taken. 

--
"I can't be around you," he mutters, his eyes darkening. I furrow my brows, taking one step closer to him, as if challenging him. 

"Why? Am I annoying to you, do you hate me?" 

"Dios mío, Valentina. Can't you leave it alone?" He says, exasperation in his tone as he rakes a hand through his hair. 

I shake my head, clenching my jaw. "Tell me. Tell me what about me you hate," I ask, my voice shaking. "Tell me why you seem to hate me when I don't even think I did anything. Tell me, Orion," I say, getting louder. 

Suddenly, he grabs my shoulders pushing me into the door. His hand darts out and he locks it. Slowly, he leans down to my ear. 

"I hate that I can't be around you without wanting to fuck the innocence right out of you," he growls. 

I am rendered speechless. He brushes his lips against my neck, and softly sucks on my sweet spot as my breath hitches. 

"Now tell me, novio, what's my name?" He says against my hot skin. 

"Papí," I moan.

title: The Vampire's Kiss
description:
We all have heard of our own share of people and creatures. But there is one more you have yet to hear about, these people have a very.....unnatural religion. Its people are united under one name, despite their inexplicably incomparable devotion; they are among the unholiest creations of God. The Vampiric Empire.

 18-year-old Andie Jordonson lives in a closed off city that feared creatures of the undead. The rules there were simple: no one goes in, no one goes out. But Creation had mercy on these people, as if to repay their generosity, each living being there was granted with unique powers to protect themselves against the vampires. The abilities usually show when they are 16, but Andie is still waiting at the age of 18. 

The city officials believed their work was done as they had just killed off all traces of the unholy community. Until one day, the most unlikely person in the world spoke out to the public. The Vampire Queen.

Or better known as, the Living Dark.

Her disciples are pitted against the human race, each vampire (in addition to their fangs) has their lips tainted in a deadly poison to paralyze their victims before sucking the blood out of them.

The Queen never goes out in public to carry out her own deeds, her disciples do all of her dirty work for her, Andie learns that she still had many supporters; so why does she suddenly decide to catch the attention of the public? Riled with curiosity and mourning a loss, Andie feels she has the need to prove herself, but she is ignorant to the cost; and the fact she hasn't unlocked her abilities yet. Then she will find herself sucked into a blood pool of madness, with the most heart accelerating surprise any mystery book fan could ever dream for.


I will help you along the way, in between the parts I will be giving you clues as to who the Living Dark is. Goodbye for now.

                                                                          ~ᗩᑭᒍ

title: The Lasts Survive
description:
Ariel Thompson, a recent -and emotionally loss - college graduate, ends up at an NFL game with old college friends. The very same college friends, who --after hundreds of peers witnessed her great humiliation -- disappeared and betrayed her. 

When a freaky thunderstorm shuts down the city and traps thousands of fans inside the stadium, not only does Ariel try to survive with her betrayers (including the guy who humiliated her, who she may still be in love with) the roof starts to collapse, a known season ticket holder wrecks havoc, fans vanish from their friends' sides, and the rebirth of an infamous urban legend causes panic no one was ready to deal with. Except one...

Tracy Earth, a mysterious woman, appearing out of the chaos around them.

*An emotional, survival-of-the-fittest, story filled with rich tension, unforgettable drama, and horrifying suspense morphed into seat-grabbing thrill, follow Ariel as she's forced to use survival skills she's never learned as both Mother Nature and foul creatures attack the stadium*

il suo nome è Elizabeth,una ragazza di sedici anni,alta,magra,con dei capelli biondo cenere e degli occhi di un blu intenso come il mare.
Era tarda sera,la prima che passasse a casa sola,finì tardi i compiti;ma prima che potesse abbandonarsi nel suo confortevole letto,sentì degli strani rumori provenire dal piano di sotto,tremante e impaurita scese le scale ma al suo arrivo nel pian terreno non vi era nessuno.
perplessa si avviò verso la sua stanza,si fermò un'istante all'ingresso: sospirò guardando il letto,si rese conto di avere più sonno del previsto,perciò entrò nella sua camera,chiuse la porta alle sue spalle ma quando si voltò una strana figura si ergeva dinanzi a lei.

   Vive en una linda casita del cerro, trabaja en un restobar frente a la playa, en su tiempo libre hace surf, los fines de semana los pasa de fiesta.  ¿Qué pasará cuando la contraten para dar clases de surf? ¿Qué sucederá ahora que estará rodeada por chicos buenos con lindos traseros surfistas y nadadores? ¿Encontrará a su Romeo, o le romperán el corazón... title: The One Who Matter Most
description:
It began with a break-up letter eight years ago. Deidre Lewis asked her best friend Delilah White to transcribe and send the letter.
Rick Bailey, newest exit from the country town of Avery, received the letter and threw it away. In his mind, he had ended his relationship with Deidre before he left town to chase his dreams.
The extra sheet of paper in that envelope began the written relationship. 
Delilah now twenty-six, was happy with her life. She found contentment in her small town teaching the kindergarten children.
Every week her excitement came from one of Rick's letters. He had attained his dreams of becoming a rock star, and she lived a vicarious life through his letters.
After a tragic death, Rick's burnt out and fed up with his existence. He needed a rest from his fans, the constant demand of recording, and he was over touring.
When Delilah offers her home as a retreat for him, neither of them is prepared for the consequences. From cheeky fathers to a deluded Deidre, his life is as crazy as when he was touring, but now he had an urge to stay. Could he convince Delilah of that truth?

title: Ever After
description:
*The final book in the Worst Heroes Ever series*

"Happily ever after," it's the most overused ending in the history of literature. Lily, the 13-year-old literature nerd, would know. She, however, knows what life is really like. She knows that not everyone gets a happy ending. Heck, her parents sure have suffered a lot, her mother still is. Lily is making this her mission. Her missing is to give her parents a normal life, if only for a little while. Except for one little problem. Lily is keeping one of her families biggest secrets. 

Book One- Worst Heroes Ever
Book Two- Burn Brighter
Book Three- Ever After
*Read first two for a better understanding, but not required*

title: Bye bye, Becky
description:
"She doesn't outshine me and she never questions my decisions or answers back. Yes, she is quite submissive but I think that's how friendship should operate. There should be someone in charge to lead the other in the right direction. Otherwise who knows where they will need up?"
                                                                                                                ~
Erin isn't popular, that's no secret. She isn't super pretty or smart. She thinks a best friend should be submissive and obedient. She doesn't have a big group of friends but doesn't really want them either. All she wants is one, perfect best friend. Becky.  She does what she is asked and never argues about it. She lives in Erin's shadow and that's how Erin likes it.

Erin's life is going fine until her principal suggests to her mom that she should leave Becky in her past and find some new friends. Suddenly Erin's perfectly constructed life starts falling apart, little by little.

Although her mother tries to explain the truth to her, she continues to  blame the world for her problems
Eventually she realises what caused her life to become undone, why it all went wrong. What the cause of all her misery is...Becky.

As she tries to track down Becky and make her pay once and for all, Erin continues to remove herself from the world and hurt the people around her. Will she realise her mistakes before it's too late? Or will she be forced into a life isolated from society completely?

                                                                                                              ~

A/n: Please don't be offended by any of the content of my story. In particular Erin's views, they are meant to be ignorant and I do not believe or support them. I just thought a very opinionated character with very debatable facts would be entertaining in a story! Ok now that we've gotten that out of the way, this is my very first story on Wattpad but I hope you enjoy it even if it's bad! Xx

title: Globular cluster 🌌💫
description:
A globular cluster is a spherical collection of stars that orbits a galactic core as a satellite. Globular clusters are very tightly bound by gravity, which gives them their spherical shapes and relatively high stellar densities toward their centers. The name of this category of star cluster is derived from the Latin globulus-a small sphere. A globular cluster is sometimes known more simply as a globular.


Life is just like a globular cluster. Were in a cluster of people and we're all supposed to be "normal" "perfect"  we sometimes don't do what we wanna do because of what people will say about us. We want to be like everyone finish school, college, get a job, get married, start a family, live happily ever after until death due us part. All of these things is what 18 year old cleo was taught  it's engrained in her mind that life is all unicorns and rainbows but she learns the sad truth that life is far from what she expected. Cleo doesn't do what she wants too do she does what she feels like other people would want her too do. She soon comes out of this habit by this particular person. Keep on reading if you want to find out how this whole mess unfolds ❤️

title: The House Guest
description:
When Helene Lovell finds herself a penniless orphan, she is swept into the world of manners, money, and etiquette, where her cruel Aunt Lady Dorothea is the ringmaster, and never ceases to remind her of her burdensome existence. The only consolation is Henry, who shows Helene friendship and kindness in a place of sadness.  Fast-forward a few years, where grown-up Henry and Helene meet again, but Helene must battle her ever growing feelings for him. As she stays as a guest at Henry's families residence, she is unwittingly submerged into the middle of family drama, tragedy, and a "love-square". Will Helene be able to overcome her social position, shyness and rank and follow her heart, or simply conform to what is expected of her?

~Dedicated to my Grandma, who recently passed away but was the best story teller I knew!~

title: Miss Incomplete
description:
In the summer before freshman year, an infamous rumor of Julian Dean grabbing a girlfriend out of all of the years he's been single, has been confirm; the heart of hopeless romantic, Francena Nakamura, had been completely shattered to the ground. She's been in love with Julian Dean for the past three years, and when the confirmed rumor spread through the city like a wildfire, Francena swore to herself to stop sending the love letters she managed to sneak in his locker every day before school, and move on. 

Now fast-forward four years and freshman Francena becomes a senior, a new rumor stirred up and its about her. 

Except, it's not. 

Julian Dean, her ex-crush, has now being receiving love letters from Francena's old pseudonym, Miss Incomplete, and they're not from her. 

And they're exactly like her notes, her style of writing, the way she would end each note, her name, even almost to her very own signature. 

Now, in a desperate attempt to stop this copycat before they reveal anymore secrets about her, she found herself partnering up with Julian Dean, to track down this imposter. 

But of course, what's meant to only be a simple task of hide and seek, she finds herself back into the situation she been trying to forget four years ago. 

And this time, he might feel the same. 

A strong might.

title: The Bad Boy (h.s)
description:
Every high school has different social classes. The jocks, the sluts, the nerds, the wannabes, and so on. Everyone has a section that they are in, but not me I'm kinda one of everything. I'm super smart, and I'm top of my class. I hang out with the popular guys and I have some friends that are considered to be apart of the sluts. I'm also kind of a wannabe in a way. I mean I want to be liked like everyone else.

     Every year, people come and go. No one really pays attention to the new kids unless they're "hot" in some way. But other than that, they are just apart of all of the weirdos in this school.

     No one was expecting him coming though. No one had a plan for him. No one knew where he went, he was like me, he was bad. He was hot. He was feared by everyone. He was my new neighbor.

     His name is Harry Styles

title: Shorty (STILL WORKING ON)
description:
4' foot 7. But everyone at Tsuyoi Gakko University makes it feels like I'm 2'7. 
Well... except Kyle.
Kyle has been my best friend since... forever. He's chill, has a casual appearance to me , but not to all the other girls. Girls think he's hot and, He's popular and I'm just... well. The short one.
Kyle is like a brother to me but for some reason a lot of people 'ship' us. And to be totally honest, I started falling for him, but ever since our first year at college , he's changed so much. He really doesn't talk to most people or act nice around most people except his little group of friends but he even gets mad at them sometimes , I'm sorta like his mom. I'm the only person he's comfortable around, I literally can talk about anything to him or tell him anything. 
Literally.
Anything.
But aside from that , he's a good person to talk to (If you really know him) when your down. 
We have tiny little fights but we will never end up not being friends, were to close.
He also knows too much.
So...
Yea.
If you don't me , my name is Ritorunelle Cha. My best friends just call me Ritoru , but if you REALLY close to me , I let you call me Ri. Like my family and Kyle. haha. Kyle.

title: Hurt Me
description:
You Never Know What A Person GoinG Through.. 

I let the tears fall as he left my room. I reached into my dresser and moved my hand around looking for my almost daily medicine. When I got it I pressed it against my arm and began to cry. I felt disgusted with myself as I did every night. Was I that beautiful or something, because no boy or grown man would want you if you were ugly right? I sobbed harder as I felt the blood dribble down my arm and leak onto the blanket. This was beginning to become to much. It's like I could still feel his hands on me and I cringed. I got up and headed to the bathroom. I ran a shower and hopped in. I made sure the water was scorching hot and scrubbed my skin as hard and as much as I can. I continued to let the tears fall as I thought back to what had just went down. Why would my stepdad want me like this?

title: Painted Skies and City Lights
description:
Exhausted from the constant bickering from her parents, Astrid decides to spend the summer with her aunt in Nantucket, Massachusetts. She hasn't been there since she was a toddler, but she still remembers the cotton candy skies and powdery sand under her toes. Her cousin has her heart set on showing Astrid how to be a real teenager. 
	Astrid soon learns that parties aren't her strong point and leaves her cousin behind to take a walk on the stunning beach. What she doesn't expect is befriending him and discovering all the things that she didn't as a child. 
	The blended skies and tours of the town are only the start of the memorable summer she needs before college.

title: Après la guerre
description: Il faisait noir. Une noirceure atroce. Personne n'arrivait à voir le mouvement de leurs mains devant leurs yeux. Une noirceure à laquelle la vision de s'habitue pas. Chacun marchait à taton, une main devant le corps, question de ne pas rencontrer quelque chose -ou quelqu'un- sans s'y attendre. L'ambiance était sinistre. Rien n'aurait pu rassurer la dizaine de garcon qui marchait en rang, le coeur de chacun d'entre eux battaient à la chamade. Le premier de rang s'arrêta, laissant les autres foncer sur lui. Il venait d'entendre quelque chose. Un craquement, du gravier qui bouge, un pas. Ses yeux se promenèrent autours de lui. Rien. Il ne voyait rien.  Il continua d'avancer, plus lentement. Jamais leur coeur n'avait battu aussi vite. Jamais avaient-ils autant regrettés leur présence ici. Jamais ils n'auraient pu prédire les prochains événements.

• Dream. 
Quite a complex word, really. Some people consider dreams to be somewhat of a fantasy. Others learn to dwell on these dreams to make them a reality. 

You've always been a dreamer. Your whole life, you've wanted to do something big - something that your heart desires. 

Growing up, you had eventually realised that those dreams don't always become a reality. You had become too comfortable in your knowledge that you don't always get what you want and now you're stuck. Stuck behind a desk in a publishing company with papers piling up everyday on your table. 

Your life seems, dull, boring, meaningless and plain. But you think to yourself, "That's what life is supposed to be."
And you think that to yourself every say of your life - until one day, you're sent on a small work trip to South Korea.

title: Please Save Me When I Become My Demon [Peter Parker x Harry Osborn]
description:
Harry Osborn is your typical rich snob who's completely obsessed with himself. He is very manipulative when it comes to the people who surround. It is his habit to ruin and humiliate those people who are weak and could not look after themselves. The demon is what people typically call him. Although Harry has an awful personality, people could not turn him away. He has such a certain charisma that draws individuals in. He has issues, anger issues, that is very destructive. However, to people around him it does not seem to matter; as long as they get to taste the pleasure of being near him, they would endure any repercussions at the end.

Peter Parker is a transfer student to Osborn High, coming from another state. Though he technically he is not foreign to the place, since he spent a good chunk of his childhood in the area, they were a lot of things that changed. When he has to suddenly move states with his parents during his younger years, he did not have the chance to better look at this place with better understanding. But now Peter is back, he has a plenty of time to do that. But what he has been waiting for so long is to reunite with his childhood best friend, Harry Osborn. He has not seen him since when he left when he was 9. He is thrilled to see him now that they obviously grow and that they are 17 this year. Peter will be starting at his new school next week Monday. Hopefully, he will bump into Harry at some point. 

How will Peter react when he found out how his best friend turned out to be?

This is a story about relationships, typical teenage issues and problems and struggles.
This story will about two men falling in love with each other. If somehow it offends you, please leave and find another story that will satisfy your needs. 

And to my future readers, enjoy people.

title: Fifty shade of grey
description:
Anastasia "Ana" Steele is a 21-year-old college senior attending Washington State University in Vancouver, Washington. Her best friend is Katherine "Kate" Kavanagh, who writes for the college newspaper. Due to an illness, Kate is unable to interview 27-year-old Christian Grey, a successful and wealthy Seattle entrepreneur, and asks Ana to take her place. Ana finds Christian attractive as well as intimidating. As a result, she stumbles through the interview and leaves Christian's office believing it went poorly. Ana does not expect to meet Christian again, but he appears at the hardware store where she works. While he purchases various items including cable ties, masking tape, and rope, Ana informs Christian that Kate would like some photographs to illustrate her article about him. Christian gives Ana his phone number. Later, Kate urges Ana to call Christian and arrange a photo shoot with their photographer friend, José Rodriguez.

The next day José, Kate, and Ana arrive for the photo shoot at the Heathman Hotel, where Christian is staying. Christian asks Ana out for coffee and asks if she is dating anyone, specifically José. Ana replies that she is not dating anyone. During the conversation, Ana learns that Christian is also single, but he says he is not romantic. Ana is intrigued but believes she is not attractive enough for Christian. Later, Ana receives a package from Christian containing first edition copies of Tess of the d'Urbervilles, which stuns her. Later that night, Ana goes out drinking with her friends and ends up drunk dialling Christian, who informs her that he will be coming to pick her up because of her inebriated state. Ana goes outside to get some fresh air, and José attempts to kiss her, but he is stopped by Christian's arrival. Ana leaves with Christian, but not before she discovers that Kate has been flirting with Christian's brother, Elliot. Later, Ana wakes to find herself in Christian's hotel room, where he scolds

Sasha Smith was an eighteen year old girl with her life completely planned out. With the perfect future upcoming, Sasha never expected to have a very dangerous encounter with the mafia underworld, and have her world turned upside down.  
  
Dragged into a spiral of crime and war, the young woman is ripped from her safe world. Forced to be part of this underworld, little did she knew that she would find the necessity to accept an agreement with a very dangerous family.  
One that would last forever: marriage. 
  
'The Scorpion' was a cold, ruthless man with a very powerful underworld empire- the heir to his father's empire. An agreement of arranged marriage was made, and Sasha finds herself in the middle of a turmoil that connects much more than simply her new marriage. 

Menacing secrets are revealed. Friends turn foe. Enemies turn allies. And Sasha learns to trust only in herself. 
  
Will she accept her new life, or will she claw her way out of that nightmare?

"Has anyone told you that you look like death?"

To everyone around her, Khloe Simmons is one of the lucky ones. She's tall and beautiful, a part of the cheerleading squad, and she has a boyfriend on all the sports teams. This fits all the criteria for teenage bliss. 

Well, no one is ever truly perfect as identified by three words.

An eating disorder.

She may not acknowledge the fact that she has one, but she definitely has it. She wants to spend her time in the summer under the radar, but she's forced to break out of her shell a bit when she meets Roman Calvert.

The tattooed nineteen year old is at his parents' house for the summertime. He's not perfect either, having some things wrong with him inside of his mind. He's labeled as the psycho of his family, but it's not nice to judge a book by its cover.

The mind is a beautiful thing, but the damage it does can be irreversible no matter what person claims can fix it.

*warning: eating disorders, mental disorders, drug use, and strong language are in this book.*

title: Lanciare una moneta
description:
E' lo stesso racconto però, al tempo stesso, sono due racconti che si guardano a distanza, che si fanno l'occhiolino, si sfiorano ma che continuano a svilupparsi separati fino alla fine.
Claudio/Mario... Mario/Claudio... 
Quale storia catturerà di più l'attenzione di chi legge?
Io penso che in questo racconto l'amore sia come una moneta che si lancia in aria... testa... croce... qualunque sia la faccia che vince, è pur sempre amore... quello vero, quello che può tutto e che è in grado di vincere tutto.
L'amore inteso come passione incontrollata che, a volte, può toglierti la pace per dar voce alle paure più recondite, che rende reale ciò che ci si sforza di nascondere.
Perché, a pensarci bene, tutti noi nascondiamo paure incontrollate nel più profondo dei nostri cuori... ma cosa succederebbe se, questi timori, trovassero la strada per venire alla luce?

title: The Everything and The Bittersweet

"Hey. I'm Athena Lock, The Everything."

*************

Athena Grace Lock is a famous dancer, singer, actress and model. (Played by Indiana Evans.) Athena is a huge fan of singer/actor Grant Gustin, and he is her celebrity crush, and gets a huge opportunity to play a character in a show he stars in, as a girl who's name is Alaska. Her hero name is Oracle, a girl who has the ability to sprout wings from her back, has heat vision, x-ray vision, and can also run at hyper speed. After a bit of time, Athena starts to fall 'like' Grant if you know what I mean. One problem... Grant is openly gay.

Thomas Grant Gustin is a famous singer/actor that stars in The CW's The Flash. Grant's celebrity crush just so happens to be a huge fan of Athena, and so when there is a new role for a superhero named Oracle, who is Grant's new love interest, Grant makes sure to save the role for Athena. (For the sake of this Fanfic, Eddie does not die, because then Barry and Iris would get married, and so Alaska and Barry couldn't be together. And also, who wouldn't ship Iris and Eddie if Barry didn't like Iris?)


Can Grant completely change his sexuality for Athena, or will Athena forever be just a girl who has a crush on a gay man. Find out in 'The Everything and The Bittersweet'

title: It Started With A Kiss
description:
No one was supposed to find out, no one.

Now I'm known as a slut, a whore, a homewrecker.

I get it. I know what I did was wrong.

I know I hurt people.

But why did it feel so right?

You want to know what happened?

I'm welcoming you into a part of my life from my point of view.

No one knows my part of the story, but I'll tell it to you now.

This is the story of how I basically ruined my life, just to have some fun.


Preview:

He walked me to my door after giving me a ride home since my boyfriend left me.

"Thanks for the ride home." I say, smiling.

"You're welcome Hana." he replies, moving a bit closer to me.

He pulls me in for a hug, then we pull away.

He looks me in the eyes and the next thing I know, his lips are on mine.

This is bad, this is so so bad. I have a boyfriend, a boyfriend. I'm kissing my boyfriend's best friend, what the fuck.

I pull away and run into my house, not saying a word.

I can't believe I just did that.

Possible triggers.

There are so many ways to fall.
You can fall in love,
Down,
Literally,
Figuratively.
The only thing they seem to have in common is that you can't
Break your own fall.
And if no one is there to break it for you,
You will land on your own fragile heart,
And it will break with the sound of
Shattering glass.
I am afraid to fall,
Because I'm afraid that I will do so alone.

title: A Piccolo Love Story ❤ (Lemon)
description:
Writing about a female Saiyan that has been on earth, but not known of. She did not know what a Saiyan was. All she knew was that she was a little different, and....has a tail. Sooner or later she runs into one of the Z Fighters and starts to form a close relationship with him... 
then she's introduced to the rest of the Z Fighters and is enlightened on her race. She becomes friends with the fighters and starts training with a certain someone, whom she starts developing feelings towards. And the other developing the same kind of sensational feelings that were unknown to him.

The past few years have been tough, especially for the Z Warriors. 
This group of fighters consisted of several strong men. 
Goku, vegeta, gohan, trunks, tien, krillin, yamcha, chiaotzu, and piccolo. 
Over the years they've battled extraordinary opponents, who have decided to try and destroy there home. Battle after battles, no breaks.
It was almost like there planet was a magnet of some sort, always attracting evil. 
These last several months it's been so quiet, and peaceful. 
This was the first break from evil the Z fighters have had in a while, all of them wishing this silence could last a life time. 
Most of the fighters took this opportunity to be lazy and slack off from training. 
Others like piccolo, and vegeta where not ones to lay back and do nothing all day. Every day they would train, if givin the chance and strengthen there body's to the maximum. 
Vegeta was very...picky? He chose to be in solitude, inside of a gravity chamber. Working his body until his muscles were torn to shreds. 
Piccolo on the other hand would always look for new ways and places to train his Mind and body, but never over worked himself to the point it would take weeks for his body to re cooperate. To him it was just a wast of time and energy.

title: The Golden Year- The Sorceress
description:
None of us can choose our destiny  but nobody can escape it either...
In this world of magic and chaos, Leila was left an orphan having no one left after a tragic fire. Over the years she learns how to use all sorts of weapons; the once sweet little girl had grown up to be a dangerous woman that didn't trust anyone. But things change drastically when Leila turns sixteen-years old and she is forced to serve the golden year.

The golden year gives the opportunity to escape the life laid out for them since birth. But Leila sees it as a nightmare. It means turning her back on her secret love, Theo. However, Leila begins to doubt her original assumptions when she gets to know Prince Leonardo.

She is pulled into the heart of a war between kingdoms at odds. She soon discovers her magical gifts and her destiny as the 'chosen one'. She never expects to learn a new truth about her own parents and about herself.  In this sweeping fantasy about Leila's journey to fulfill her destiny and all the monsters that stand in her way. Only one monster does not have fangs or claws but he does have a powerful hold on her heart. 

Danger and betrayal, forbidden love and lust, dark secrets and enchantments threaten Leila's life and it could lead to her ultimate destruction. 
Not your average fairytale...
"I am powerful. I am dangerous.  I am lethal."

Currently on 22nd Volume

Yza Blade is your typical high-school student, whose fate encounter with the "Stardust Knight" clan changes his life forever in ways that cannot be explained. Whilst Yza is having fun with Cardfight!! Vanguard, a group of cardfighters known as the "Reverse" are following orders from the Void to break the barrier that separates Earth from Cray.
